|start date=Fall [[2000]]<ref name="Date">''[[Star Wars Gamer Special Edition]]'' is a preview issue of ''Star Wars Gamer'', which was announced on [[June 29]], [[2000]] and whose first issue was released in [[November]]. The first issue of the magazine did not complete production until approximately [[August]] or [[September]], according to {{Wizards|url=starwars/article.asp?x=adayinthelife,2&c=gamer|text=A Day in the Life of ''Star Wars Gamer''}}. Thus, the preview issue was released sometime between then and November.</ref>
|end date=[[May 7]], [[2002]]<ref name="SW.com">{{SWArchive|url=gaming/other/rpg/news20020416.html|text=Episode II in Gamer #10}}</ref>
|genre=
|issues=10
}}
'''''Star Wars Gamer''''' was a bi-monthly magazine published by [[Wizards of the Coast]], focusing on all forms of ''[[Star Wars]]'' gaming, including [[roleplaying game]]s, [[Star Wars video games|video game]]s, board games, etc. It ran from [[November]] [[2000]] to [[May]] [[2002]].

